LB_mean = df['LB'].mean()
AC_mean = df['AC'].mean()
DS_mean = df['DS'].mean()
DP_mean = df['DP'].mean()
MLTV_mean = df['MLTV'].mean()
Width_mean = df['Width'].mean()
Tendency_mean = df['Tendency'].mean()
NSP_mean = df['NSP'].mean()

print(LB_mean,AC_mean,DS_mean,DP_mean,MLTV_mean,Width_mean,Tendency_mean,NSP_mean)

# Outliers Detection

Q1 = df.quantile(0.25)
Q2 = df.quantile(0.50)
Q3 = df.quantile(0.75)

IQR = Q3-Q1
print('Old Shape',IQR)
upper = Q3+1.5*IQR
print('Upper :', upper)
lower = Q3-1.5*IQR
print('Lower :', lower)
